snippet.title: DreadOut Keepers Of The Dark Story Trailer
snippet.description:
DreadOut: Keepers of the Dark is a new standalone horror game that takes place in the DreadOut universe.  Available on March 24, 2016. http://store.steampowered.com/app/418950

In this missing chapter, you will help Linda face the challenges of the DreadOut world with even more dangers lurking within.

DreadOut steam store page : http://store.steampowered.com/app/269790
DreadOut Official Merchandise : http://store.dreadout.com/
